

## 什么是同源策略

**同源策略**是一个重要的安全策略，它用于限制一个[origin](https://link.segmentfault.com/?enc=WRdw7AGa0xXjvqeTmwNKCg%3D%3D.io3AErVfGDaRhNGpr4jsB%2F%2Fm9ngD2osTL33NKK6ue5QcL6lYQSQX9C6qXaIEKNZbxAkb8RodAd8ENzZoz7E24w%3D%3D)的文档或者它加载的脚本如何能与另一个源的资源进行交互。它能帮助阻隔恶意文档，减少可能被攻击的媒介。

只有当**protocol（协议）、domain（域名）、port（端口）三者一致**，才是同源。

跨域资源共享([CORS](https://link.segmentfault.com/?enc=50kfxFQr6URaJEXui8NTgg%3D%3D.Fc7k0eWYxZa9W5q6B8YQvoD4fLH4tAvs5CVRxAaCVjln9iW5LoJ4JEqeQcAVFum69CTaKJ6ff%2FFtW85Xe1JsNg%3D%3D)) 是一种机制，它使用额外的[HTTP](https://link.segmentfault.com/?enc=n4ZZ9u3z2oXV%2FftVXv%2Fxhg%3D%3D.fTZ2IJLWhNGGrFH8fEolVxx8a4FlguR6%2BgnYEkyoPZqQ9%2FXDPWivssamG2S7ELHbGOA13%2FIhSmV8Tii8616wfQ%3D%3D)头来告诉浏览器 让运行在一个 origin (domain) 上的 Web 应用被准许访问来自不同源服务器上的指定的资源。当一个资源从与该资源本身所在的服务器**不同的域、协议或端口**请求一个资源时，资源会发起一个**跨域 HTTP 请求**。




## 模拟跨域请求
**1. 创建测试网站**

```shell
mkdir -p /usr/share/nginx/web1
vim /usr/share/nginx/web1/index.html
```

```html
<html>
<head>
    <title>web1</title>
    <script type='text/javascript'>
        var xmlhttp = new XMLHttpRequest()
        xmlhttp.open("GET", "http://web2.example.com/index.html", true);
        xmlhttp.send();
    </script>
</head>
<body style="padding: 20px;">
    <h1>Heare is Web1</h1>
    <p>跨域请求web2...</p>
</body>
</html>
```
```shell
mkdir -p /usr/share/nginx/web2
vim /usr/share/nginx/web2/index.html
```

```html
<html>
<head>
    <title>web2</title>
</head>
<script type='text/javascript'>
    var xmlhttp = new XMLHttpRequest()
    xmlhttp.open("GET", "http://web1.example.com/index.html", true);
    xmlhttp.send();
</script>
<body style="padding: 20px;">
    <h1>Heare is Web2</h1>
    <p>跨域请求web1...</p>
</body>
</html>
```

**2. 配置nginx**

```shell
vim /etc/nginx/conf.d/cors-example.conf
```

```nginx
server {
  listen 80;
  server_name web1.example.com;

  location / {
    root /usr/share/nginx/web1;
    index index.html index.htm;
  }
}

server {
  listen 80;
  server_name web2.example.com;

  location / {
    root /usr/share/nginx/web2;
    index index.html index.htm;
  }
}
```

**3. 配置Hosts**

```shell
vim /etc/hosts
127.0.0.1 web1.example.com
127.0.0.1 web2.example.com
```

**4. 重启Nginx**

```shell
nginx -t
nginx -s reload
```

## 解决跨域问题

```nginx
server {
  listen 80;
  server_name web1.example.com;

  location / {
    # 设置跨域
    add_header 'Access-Control-Allow-Origin' *;
    add_header 'Access-Control-Allow-Credentials' 'true';
    add_header 'Access-Control-Allow-Methods' *;
    add_header 'Access-Control-Allow-Headers' *;

    root /usr/share/nginx/web1;
    index index.html index.htm;
  }
}

server {
  listen 80;
  server_name web2.example.com;

  #【推荐】限定跨域范围（仅允许*.example.com和*.example.org跨域请求）
  location / {
    # 设置跨域
    if ($http_origin ~* (https?://(.*\.)?(example\.com|example\.org))) {
      add_header Access-Control-Allow-Origin $http_origin;
    }
    add_header 'Access-Control-Allow-Credentials' 'true';
    add_header 'Access-Control-Allow-Methods' *;
    add_header 'Access-Control-Allow-Headers' *;

    root /usr/share/nginx/web2;
    index index.html index.htm;
  }
}
```
